HEADWORD: Jew
<hw>Jew</hw> <pr>(j⟦umac⟧ <it>or</it> j⟦oomac⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Of or pertaining to Jews; Jewish; -- usually considered
offensive.</def> <mark>[offensive]</mark> ⟦br⟧
